        <abstract> 
<p>JM will publish [<hi rend="italic">Variation</hi>] "coute qui coute", paying CD half the profits.</p>  
<p>Thinks he can count on 500 purchases of what he calls the "Pièces Justificatives" of the <hi rend="italic">Origin</hi> and will print 750 copies.</p> 
            <p>His literary friend found it "difficult of digestion".</p>
